  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    School governance update
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Important news and communications from the Department for Education (DfE) relating to governance in maintained schools and academy trusts in England.</p>

  </div>
</div>

